data.meta_site_name: Smith College Club of the Peninsula
data.text: Smith College has a remarkable story to tell. It is a story of leadership, of women helping women, and using the power of education and community to make a better world. Smith today is vibrant and innovative. Smith students are bold and creative thinkers. Smith graduates are driven, passionate changemakers. There is a lot to be excited about: the renovation of Neilson Library, Smith's Year on Climate Change initiative, and our Here For Every Voice campaign to raise $75 million in scholarship aid for students.
